#: data/experimental/units.ruleset:1267 data/multiplayer/units.ruleset:1344
#: data/royale/units.ruleset:1574 data/sandbox/units.ruleset:1427
msgid "Artillery"
msgstr "포"

#: data/civ1/units.ruleset:805
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The artillery is an upgraded cannon with improved defensive as well as "
"offensive capabilities. It can shoot over city walls, ignoring their effect."
msgstr ""
"곡사포는 공격 능력뿐만 아니라 방어의 향상과 함께, 포에서 개선된 것입니다."

#: data/civ1/units.ruleset:812 data/civ2/units.ruleset:1265
#: data/civ2civ3/units.ruleset:1489 data/classic/units.ruleset:1310
#: data/experimental/units.ruleset:1333 data/multiplayer/units.ruleset:1410
#: data/royale/units.ruleset:1643 data/sandbox/units.ruleset:1493
