#: data/multiplayer/units.ruleset:945 data/royale/units.ruleset:1151
#: data/sandbox/units.ruleset:1014
msgid "Marines are infantry who are experts at marine warfare."
msgstr "해병은 해상 전투에 전문가인 보병입니다."

#: data/civ2/units.ruleset:831 data/classic/units.ruleset:940
#: data/multiplayer/units.ruleset:976
msgid ""
"Paratroopers are experts at airborne attacks. From a friendly city or "
"airbase, Paratroopers who have not expended any movement points can paradrop "
"directly to any tile in range, and be immediately ready to act there. "
"(Beware dropping into unseen territory, as Paratroopers landing on a tile "
"occupied by enemy units are easy targets!)"
msgstr ""

#: data/civ2/units.ruleset:868 data/classic/units.ruleset:977
#: data/experimental/units.ruleset:1000 data/multiplayer/units.ruleset:1013
msgid ""
"The Mechanized Infantry has the strongest defensive strength of any land "
"unit, but is only available near the end of the technology tree."
msgstr ""
"기계화 보병은 어느 지상 부대보다 가장 강한 방어력을 가졌지만, 기술 나무의 끝"
"의 근처에 도달해야만 유효합니다."

#: data/civ2/units.ruleset:875 data/civ2civ3/units.ruleset:1089
#: data/classic/units.ruleset:984 data/experimental/units.ruleset:1007
#: data/multiplayer/units.ruleset:1020 data/royale/units.ruleset:1232
#: data/sandbox/units.ruleset:1093
msgid "Horsemen"
msgstr "기수"

#: data/civ2/units.ruleset:901 data/civ2civ3/units.ruleset:1115
#: data/classic/units.ruleset:1010 data/experimental/units.ruleset:1033
#: data/multiplayer/units.ruleset:1046 data/royale/units.ruleset:1258
#: data/sandbox/units.ruleset:1119
msgid ""
"Horsemen are mounted warriors and an early shock-troop that can penetrate "
