#: data/civ2/units.ruleset:1877 data/civ2civ3/units.ruleset:2129
#: data/classic/units.ruleset:1925 data/experimental/units.ruleset:1952
#: data/multiplayer/units.ruleset:2024 data/royale/units.ruleset:2550
#: data/sandbox/units.ruleset:2141
#, fuzzy
