#, fuzzy
msgid "Operative"
msgstr "활동중"

#: data/royale/units.ruleset:2944
msgid ""
"An Operative is more skilled in the arts of espionage than her Diplomat "
"predecessor or the Spy."
msgstr ""

#: data/royale/units.ruleset:2946
msgid ""
"Operatives will be able to use many means for trasportation and will ignore "
"terrain when moving. She can perform all the functions of the Spy. Refer to "
"the Spy and Diplomat entries for more details. Unlike a Diplomat, an "
"Operative may also survive an operation in a foreign city and become more "
"experienced as a result. Operatives are also more effective than Diplomats "
"at defending cities against foreign Diplomats, Spies and Operatives. If you "
"steal a random tech, the probability for succeeding is a probability between "
"0-1 and it is typically something like 0.08- 0.12. However if you choose a "
"tech to be stolen the chance to succeed is much lower and is n*n instead of "
"n. With the  probability of 0.08 the chance to succeed to steal a specific "
